data.description: This light and airy two story home has a half bath, large kitchen and an open and spacious dining and living room with a beautiful fireplace and a laundry area on the first floor, along with an insulated large enclosed sunroom!! The second story has 3 bedrooms with 2 baths and great views of the mountains. Hardwood flooring downstairs with oak cabinets in the kitchen. Coffered ceilings and the main en suite has a soaking tub, shower and large walkin closet. On a large corner lot with a covered front porch you can enjoy the outdoors. New roof in 2021. The fenced back yard allows for privacy and the cul de sac keeps traffic to a minimum.  Nice subdivision with a country feel away from town!! Property is eligible for 100% financing with a USDA Loan.
